{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_01","textHome":"你好。我是时雨，宫尾时雨。我以前是黑羽，@然后我喜欢育梦。还有，我喜欢机器人，自@己也会做一点点。我不是很擅长说话，所以@差不多可以了吧？和不认识的人说话很容易@累，还是请你快走吧。对不起。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":10.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_17","textHome":"机器人编程中，似乎可以使用各种各样的语言@。虽然像C语言还有Python之类的，@净是些我不明白的东西就是了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_18","textHome":"虽然刚开始接触编程，但总有一天，我想做出@个带着光学传感器的那种帅气的机器人来。@我还想在机器人竞赛上得奖。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_19","textHome":"既然弱小，就以数量取胜。这是我的最大火力@，所以绝对不会打偏。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_20","textHome":"我已经脱掉了黑羽的斗篷。之后，我会稍微变@强一点的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_21","textHome":"明明成为了魔法少女，但我甚至没有足以生存@下去的力量。即便如此，我也感觉自己克服@了一点点胆小的毛病。所以，我会更加努力@的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_22","textHome":"灯花大人说过的话语。表明魔法少女要更加优@越的那些话语。它们都一直活在我的心中。@所以，我想要告诉大家。虽然还做不到站立@于其他人之上，但如果能一起实现理想就好@了啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_23","textHome":"姬有着领导他人的力量。而且，她也会告诉全@世界，我们是被选中的存在。所以，我会为@了姬使用这份力量。就算是现在也毫无后悔@。这比我独自埋头于数字世界要好太多了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_24","textHome":"又来了……就算不特意找我交谈也没事的哦。@我也没有和你交谈的意思，所以你还是去那@边吧。诶，要留在这里吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_25","textHome":"到早上了……肚子好饿……冰箱里放了些什么@来着。就吃酸奶可以吗。会不会被妈妈骂呢@。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_26","textHome":"我不讨厌自己一个人待着，所以你去那边吧。@我会自己享用饭菜的。……啊呜，嗯，妈妈@做的便当今天也很好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_02","textHome":"我是时雨，宫尾时雨。我不是很喜欢其他人。@但是，我会试着去习惯的。就是这样。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_27","textHome":"就算是在放学之后，也能听见机械的声音。工@匠学舍的声音就像有生命一样，我很喜欢。@就算是无机物也有生命，就是这种感觉。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_28","textHome":"就算只是慢慢地，我也要不断扩散。“魔法少@女很厉害”“比普通人类要更优越”这些事@情。所以晚上我会偷偷行动，增加自己的同@伴。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_29","textHome":"1、2、3，最后一击！至少要把空闲时间拿@来练习战斗才行。因为我不想拖别人的后腿@……我想集中一下，所以你还是走吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_30","textHome":"是魔女……有魔女……虽然会稍微有点紧张，@但我比之前更强了，就算靠自己也能打倒。@但是，如果有其他人在，我应该会更高兴…@…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界。我在那里看见了自己的复制品。虽@然是个自信满满的假货，但我也不禁想到，@希望自己也能变得那么强大。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_32","textHome":"如果要以集团战斗，我不上前也可以吧？我比@较擅长从远距离狙击。所以，支援就交给我@吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_33","textHome":"嗯，我确实是原黑羽。如果讨厌玛吉斯之翼的@话，别接近我就好了。反正我又阴暗又阴沉@……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_34","textHome":"你知道这个键盘吗！？诶，啊……没什么。它@的打击感很好，所以我很喜欢……不过，这@个是从爷爷那里收到的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_35","textHome":"虽然我打游戏打得不是很多，但稍微有点喜欢@。VR游戏可以沉浸式体验，所以我尤其喜@欢。因为可以在开放世界里成为另一个自己@。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_36","textHome":"诶，我完全不困就是了……因为我的睡眠时间@本来就很短。现在我也很清醒，完全没有问@题。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_03","textHome":"我很讨厌妈妈，但也很喜欢她……大概，非常@喜欢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_37","textHome":"你愿意夸奖我吗？如果愿意的话，就来夸奖我@吧。要夸很多哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_38","textHome":"呵呵，育梦的膝枕很软也很舒服呢。舒服到就@算是平时不怎么睡觉的我，也能美美地睡一@觉。虽然很推荐，但除我以外的人都不许做@。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_39","textHome":"妈妈好像又和不认识的男人待在一起……我听@说爷爷去接她了……虽然肯定不会发生太糟@糕的事情，但果然还是很担心……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900,"motion":0}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_40","textHome":"呐，你知道吗？听说魔法少女比普通人类更优@越这件事情，是被历史证明过的。灯花大人@和音梦大人都这么说过。这就是我的希望。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_41","textHome":"我能彻底相信的人很少。但是，或许你可以进@入那个范畴。不，我什么也没说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_42","textHome":"如果是现在的我，肯定……"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_43","textHome":"好，这样就结束了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_44","textHome":"3、2、1，好了，出局。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_45","textHome":"这样，我是不是就稍微接近了一点理想？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_46","textHome":"我已经走到了再也无法后退的地方哦。"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_04","textHome":"育梦的手，非常暖和……"}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_05","textHome":"对大部分弱者来说，变成这样的契机都是一样@的。"}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_13","textHome":"就算像我一样弱小，也能着实地感觉到自己变@强了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_14","textHome":"我已经成长到连魔女也能打倒了，心情好激动@啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_15","textHome":"这些事，我不会跟其他人说。都是特别讲给你@听的，所以要保密哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102900,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_16","textHome":"我喜欢做机器人。虽然也才刚刚起步……但是@，我会把从爷爷那里得到的电路板之类的材@料固定在丙烯酸树脂板上使用哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}]},"version":3}